{
  "_comment_header": [
    "Canonical declarative spec for the Geopolitical Intelligence PoC",
    "Workshop module 'Geopolitical Intel Workbench'. SOURCE OF TRUTH for",
    "the rows the operator POSTs to application-composition-service via:",
    "",
    "  POST  /api/v1/apps                          (create the app)",
    "  PATCH /api/v1/apps/{id}                     (update pages / settings)",
    "  POST  /api/v1/apps/{id}/publish             (promote to published)",
    "",
    "Foundry-native framing",
    "-----------------------",
    "Per the Workshop concepts-widgets page, a module is declarative JSON:",
    "variables + sections + widgets + layout. The 19 widget types this",
    "module uses are all in the v1 widget catalog (Gap 1 closed). The",
    "vertex_graph_embed widget renders an Object-Explorer-equivalent",
    "graph that lives in OpenFoundry's Vertex-equivalent app —",
    "Workshop embeds a saved graph by RID per the embed page.",
    "",
    "References (all in 00-contrato-foundry-native.md baseline):",
    "  - https://www.palantir.com/docs/foundry/workshop/concepts-widgets",
    "  - https://www.palantir.com/docs/foundry/workshop/widgets-object-table",
    "  - https://www.palantir.com/docs/foundry/workshop/widgets-map/",
    "  - https://www.palantir.com/docs/foundry/workshop/widgets-button-group/",
    "  - https://www.palantir.com/docs/foundry/workshop/widgets-embed-foundry-apps/",
    "  - https://www.palantir.com/docs/foundry/workshop/branching-rebasing/",
    "",
    "Branching caveat",
    "-----------------",
    "Per the Workshop branching docs, the vertex_graph_embed and agent",
    "widgets are NOT editable on a Workshop branch — only the surrounding",
    "widgets are. The UC-6 branch demo MUST avoid edits to these two and",
    "demonstrate the branch experience through the editable widgets",
    "(filter_list, object_table, map, timeline, button_group).",
    "",
    "Vertex graph dependency",
    "------------------------",
    "vertex_graph_embed needs an existing saved Vertex graph RID. The",
    "operator MUST create the 'Actor neighborhood' saved graph in the",
    "Vertex-equivalent app BEFORE registering this module, and patch",
    "the placeholder rid below (vertexGraphRid default) with the real",
    "RID. The register script surfaces this prereq explicitly."
  ],

  "name": "Geopolitical Intel Workbench",
  "slug": "geopolitical-intel-workbench",
  "branch": "main",
  "description": "Interactive analyst workbench: filters + Actor table + Map + Timeline + Vertex graph + AIP copilot + Action buttons. Configured (not coded) via application-composition-service. Inherits the caller's markings end-to-end.",
  "status": "draft",
  "template_key": null,

  "theme": {
    "name": "geopolitica-default",
    "accent": "navy",
    "footer_attributions": [
      "Source: GDELT Project — gdeltproject.org. CC-BY.",
      "Source: ACLED — acleddata.com. Non-commercial use; attribution required.",
      "Source: U.S. Treasury OFAC SDN list (public domain).",
      "Source: EU Consolidated Sanctions List — Council of the EU.",
      "Source: OpenSanctions — opensanctions.org. CC-BY 4.0.",
      "Source: Wikidata — wikidata.org. CC0."
    ]
  },

  "settings": {
    "navigation_style": "tabs",
    "max_width": "1440px",
    "show_branding": true,
    "home_page_id": "workbench",
    "workshop_variables": [
      {
        "id": "selectedActor",
        "kind": "object",
        "name": "Selected actor",
        "object_type_id": "Actor",
        "source_widget_id": "actor-object-table"
      },
      {
        "id": "selectedActorSet",
        "kind": "object_set",
        "name": "Filtered actor set",
        "object_type_id": "Actor",
        "source_widget_id": "actor-filter-list",
        "metadata": {
          "use_search_backend": true,
          "_comment_use_search_backend": "B03 G2 — route Workshop reads for this object_set through POST /api/v1/ontology/search (Vespa-backed) instead of the Cassandra-backed object-database query. Required for Act 4 in 11-guion-demo.md against GDELT-scale rows. Honoured by resolveUseSearchBackend() in apps/web/src/lib/components/apps/widgets/workshopObjectSets.ts."
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "selectedTimeWindow",
        "kind": "timestamp_range",
        "name": "Date window",
        "default_value": {"start": "now-72h", "end": "now"}
      },
      {
        "id": "vertexGraphRid",
        "kind": "string",
        "name": "Saved Vertex graph RID",
        "default_value": "ri.vertex.main.graph.PLACEHOLDER-actor-neighborhood",
        "metadata": {
          "operator_note": "Replace with the real RID from the Vertex-equivalent app's 'Actor neighborhood' saved graph before publishing."
        }
      }
    ]
  },

  "pages": [
    {
      "id": "workbench",
      "name": "Workbench",
      "path": "/",
      "description": "Main analyst workbench page.",
      "visible": true,
      "layout": {"kind": "grid", "columns": 12, "gap": "1rem", "max_width": "1440px"},

      "widgets": [
        {
          "id": "header-title",
          "widget_type": "text",
          "title": "Title",
          "description": "",
          "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 8, "height": 2},
          "props": {
            "content": "# Geopolitical Intel Workbench\nFilter, pivot, and act on Actors / Events / Sanctions / News with the AIP copilot in-pane.",
            "align": "left"
          },
          "events": [],
          "children": []
        },

        {
          "id": "header-agent",
          "widget_type": "agent",
          "title": "AIP Copilot",
          "description": "Embedded geopolitical analyst copilot.",
          "position": {"x": 8, "y": 0, "width": 4, "height": 4},
          "props": {
            "agent_id": "geopolitica-analyst-copilot",
            "welcome_message": "Ask about actors, events, or sanctions. I read the selected actor + date window from the panel.",
            "submit_label": "Ask"
          },
          "events": [],
          "children": []
        }
      ],

      "sections": [
        {
          "id": "left-col-filters-and-table",
          "title": "",
          "layout": {"kind": "grid", "columns": 12, "gap": "0.75rem"},
          "widgets": [
            {
              "id": "actor-filter-list",
              "widget_type": "filter_list",
              "title": "Actor filters",
              "description": "Filter the Actor set by country, sanctioned-only, kind.",
              "position": {"x": 0, "y": 4, "width": 5, "height": 4},
              "props": {
                "source_variable_id": "selectedActorSet",
                "output_variable_id": "selectedActorSet",
                "layout": "vertical",
                "allow_add_remove": false,
                "filters": [
                  {"property": "country_iso2", "control": "multi_select", "label": "Country"},
                  {"property": "is_sanctioned", "control": "toggle",       "label": "Sanctioned only"},
                  {"property": "kind",          "control": "multi_select", "label": "Actor kind",
                    "options": ["PERSON", "ORG", "ARMED_GROUP", "GOV"]}
                ]
              },
              "bindings": [
                {"source_type": "ontology", "source_id": "Actor", "fields": ["actor_id", "display_name", "country_iso2", "is_sanctioned", "kind"], "parameters": {}}
              ],
              "events": [],
              "children": []
            },

            {
              "id": "actor-object-table",
              "widget_type": "object_table",
              "title": "Actors",
              "description": "Actor rows matching the current filters. Click selects an Actor.",
              "position": {"x": 0, "y": 8, "width": 5, "height": 6},
              "props": {
                "source_variable_id": "selectedActorSet",
                "active_object_variable_id": "selectedActor",
                "default_sort_property": "event_count_30d",
                "default_sort_direction": "desc",
                "row_height_lines": 2,
                "wrap_values": false,
                "multi_select": false,
                "columns": [
                  {"property": "display_name",     "label": "Name",       "width": 220},
                  {"property": "kind",             "label": "Kind",       "width": 90},
                  {"property": "country_iso2",     "label": "Country",    "width": 70},
                  {"property": "is_sanctioned",    "label": "Sanctioned", "width": 90},
                  {"property": "event_count_30d",  "label": "Events/30d", "width": 90}
                ]
              },
              "bindings": [
                {"source_type": "variable", "source_id": "selectedActorSet", "fields": ["actor_id", "display_name", "kind", "country_iso2", "is_sanctioned", "event_count_30d"], "parameters": {}}
              ],
              "events": [
                {"id": "row-click", "trigger": "row_click", "action": "set_variable",
                  "label": "Select actor",
                  "config": {"variable_id": "selectedActor", "value_path": "$.row.object"}}
              ],
              "children": []
            },

            {
              "id": "actor-property-list",
              "widget_type": "property_list",
              "title": "Actor detail",
              "description": "Properties of the selected actor.",
              "position": {"x": 0, "y": 14, "width": 5, "height": 4},
              "props": {
                "source_variable_id": "selectedActor",
                "number_of_columns": 2,
                "hide_nulls": true,
                "value_layout": "adjacent",
                "properties": [
                  {"property": "display_name"},
                  {"property": "kind"},
                  {"property": "country_iso2"},
                  {"property": "is_sanctioned"},
                  {"property": "wikidata_qid"},
                  {"property": "event_count_30d"},
                  {"property": "last_seen_at_utc"},
                  {"property": "reliability_score"}
                ]
              },
              "bindings": [
                {"source_type": "variable", "source_id": "selectedActor",
                  "fields": ["display_name", "kind", "country_iso2", "is_sanctioned", "wikidata_qid", "event_count_30d", "last_seen_at_utc", "reliability_score"],
                  "parameters": {}}
              ],
              "events": [],
              "children": []
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "id": "center-col-visualizations",
          "title": "",
          "layout": {"kind": "grid", "columns": 12, "gap": "0.75rem"},
          "widgets": [
            {
              "id": "events-map",
              "widget_type": "map",
              "title": "Events",
              "description": "Event points coloured by CAMEO quad-class; Actor pins iconified by kind.",
              "position": {"x": 5, "y": 4, "width": 7, "height": 5},
              "props": {
                "base_layer_kind": "raster",
                "base_tile_url": "https://tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png",
                "center_lat": 48.5,
                "center_lon": 32.0,
                "zoom": 4,
                "show_legend": true,
                "layers": [
                  {
                    "id": "events-layer",
                    "title": "Events",
                    "source": "object_type",
                    "object_type_id": "Event",
                    "loading_mode": "viewport_tiles",
                    "geometry_type": "point",
                    "latitude_field": "action_geo_lat",
                    "longitude_field": "action_geo_lon",
                    "label_field": "title",
                    "color": "#d6433c",
                    "visible": true,
                    "cluster_enabled": true
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "actors-layer",
                    "title": "Actors",
                    "source": "variable",
                    "source_variable_id": "selectedActorSet",
                    "geometry_type": "point",
                    "latitude_field": "hq_lat",
                    "longitude_field": "hq_lon",
                    "label_field": "display_name",
                    "color": "#2d72d2",
                    "visible": true,
                    "cluster_enabled": false
                  }
                ],
                "time_configuration": {
                  "enabled": true,
                  "open_by_default": false,
                  "time_zone": "utc",
                  "time_format": "24h",
                  "event_time_field": "event_time_utc",
                  "time_window_start_variable_id": "selectedTimeWindow.start",
                  "time_window_end_variable_id": "selectedTimeWindow.end"
                },
                "output_variable_id": "selectedActor"
              },
              "events": [],
              "children": []
            },

            {
              "id": "events-timeline",
              "widget_type": "timeline",
              "title": "Event timeline",
              "description": "Events bucketed by date, coloured by source.",
              "position": {"x": 5, "y": 9, "width": 7, "height": 4},
              "props": {
                "orientation": "horizontal",
                "order": "newest_first",
                "show_legend": true,
                "show_time_between_events": false,
                "highlight_selection": true,
                "max_events": 2000,
                "layers": [
                  {
                    "id": "events-by-source",
                    "title": "Events",
                    "source_variable_id": "selectedActorSet",
                    "object_type_id": "Event",
                    "date_property": "event_time_utc",
                    "title_mode": "property",
                    "title_property": "title",
                    "properties_mode": "specific",
                    "displayed_properties": ["cameo_code", "source", "country_iso2"],
                    "color_mode": "dynamic",
                    "color": "#2d72d2",
                    "color_rules": [
                      {"property_name": "source", "operator": "equals", "value": "GDELT", "color": "#2d72d2"},
                      {"property_name": "source", "operator": "equals", "value": "ACLED", "color": "#cf662f"}
                    ],
                    "icon_mode": "default",
                    "icon": "calendar"
                  }
                ],
                "selected_object_variable_id": "selectedActor"
              },
              "events": [],
              "children": []
            },

            {
              "id": "actor-vertex-graph",
              "widget_type": "vertex_graph_embed",
              "title": "Actor neighborhood (Vertex)",
              "description": "Saved Vertex graph centred on the selected Actor.",
              "position": {"x": 5, "y": 13, "width": 7, "height": 5},
              "props": {
                "resource": {
                  "kind": "variable",
                  "variable_id": "vertexGraphRid"
                },
                "selected_objects_variable_id": "selectedActor",
                "zoom_to_variable_id": "selectedActor",
                "append_on_parameter_change": false,
                "parameters": [
                  {"id": "actorId", "kind": "object_set", "variable_id": "selectedActor"}
                ],
                "available_actions": "some",
                "available_action_type_ids": ["add-to-watchlist", "flag-actor", "open-investigation-case"],
                "capabilities": {
                  "read_only": false,
                  "enable_transition_to_vertex": true,
                  "enable_export_png": true
                },
                "panels": {
                  "legend": true,
                  "selection": true,
                  "info": true,
                  "search": true,
                  "subgraph_navigation": true,
                  "timeline": false,
                  "series": false,
                  "time_selection": false,
                  "layers": false,
                  "histogram": false,
                  "version_history": false,
                  "add_object": false
                },
                "incomplete_inputs_message": "Select an Actor in the table to centre the graph."
              },
              "events": [],
              "children": []
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "id": "bottom-actions",
          "title": "",
          "layout": {"kind": "toolbar", "columns": 12, "gap": "0.5rem"},
          "widgets": [
            {
              "id": "action-button-group",
              "widget_type": "button_group",
              "title": "Actions",
              "description": "All writes flow through ontology-actions-service and require confirmation.",
              "position": {"x": 0, "y": 18, "width": 12, "height": 2},
              "props": {
                "orientation": "horizontal",
                "buttons": [
                  {
                    "id": "btn-add-to-watchlist",
                    "label": "Add to Watchlist",
                    "intent": "primary",
                    "action_id": "act-add-to-watchlist",
                    "disabled_when": {"variable_unset": "selectedActor"}
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "btn-flag-actor",
                    "label": "Flag Actor",
                    "intent": "warning",
                    "action_id": "act-flag-actor",
                    "disabled_when": {"variable_unset": "selectedActor"}
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "btn-open-case",
                    "label": "Open Investigation Case",
                    "intent": "danger",
                    "action_id": "act-open-investigation-case",
                    "disabled_when": {"variable_unset": "selectedActor"},
                    "role_required": "compliance"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "actions": [
                {
                  "id": "act-add-to-watchlist",
                  "kind": "submit_action_type",
                  "action_type_id": "add-to-watchlist",
                  "label": "Add to Watchlist",
                  "config": {
                    "require_confirmation": true,
                    "context_variable_id": "selectedActor",
                    "parameters": {"actor_id": "$.selectedActor.actor_id"}
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "act-flag-actor",
                  "kind": "submit_action_type",
                  "action_type_id": "flag-actor",
                  "label": "Flag Actor",
                  "config": {
                    "require_confirmation": true,
                    "context_variable_id": "selectedActor",
                    "parameters": {"actor_id": "$.selectedActor.actor_id"}
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "act-open-investigation-case",
                  "kind": "submit_action_type",
                  "action_type_id": "open-investigation-case",
                  "label": "Open Investigation Case",
                  "config": {
                    "require_confirmation": true,
                    "context_variable_id": "selectedActor",
                    "parameters": {"actor_id": "$.selectedActor.actor_id"}
                  }
                }
              ],
              "events": [
                {"id": "btn-click", "trigger": "click", "action": "run_action",
                  "config": {"action_id": "$.button.action_id"}}
              ],
              "children": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],

  "_acceptance": [
    "App appears in GET /api/v1/apps with name 'Geopolitical Intel Workbench'.",
    "Every widget renders without console errors at GET /apps/geopolitical-intel-workbench — including the vertex_graph_embed (which requires the saved-graph RID to be patched).",
    "Click on a row in actor-object-table → actor-property-list updates, events-map re-centres on the actor's HQ, events-timeline filters to the actor, and actor-vertex-graph re-centres.",
    "Click on 'Add to Watchlist' opens the confirmation dialog for action.add_to_watchlist; submitting writes a row to the Action Log.",
    "Marcos's session shows OFAC-restricted Actor rows as placeholders (the marking filter is applied server-side by object-database-service before the row reaches the widget)."
  ]
}
